  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"RepairQ1.21.4-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Fixed an issue that caused an \u2018Import failed\u2019 message when importing catalog items.</p></li><li><p>Resolved an issue where the location scope for Catalog Items was incorrectly changing from \u2018Global\u2019 to \u2018Location' after saving changes, causing some items to disappear from view in the catalog.</p></li><li><p>Resolved an issue where the effective tax-inclusive price for Inventory Labels ignored the tax-inclusive app setting, adding tax to an already tax-inclusive price.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue where adding a partial cash payment incorrectly set the ticket balance to $0. Now, only the entered payment amount will be applied, ensuring the remaining balance is correctly reflected.</p></li><li><p>Resolved an issue where the \u2018Not a Customer Yet\u2019 checkbox was not syncing between the General and Misc tabs when creating a Customer Profile. Now, any change made in one tab will automatically update in the other.</p></li><li><p>Resolved an issue where searching for a customer name containing an apostrophe in the Contacts search field caused a 500 error.</p></li><li><p>Fixed an issue where Supplier SKUs were not appearing in the catalog item view. Catalog items with an assigned Supplier SKU are now visible in the Catalog Item list.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
